284
00:24:52,991 --> 00:24:54,534
My brothers and sisters, they…

285
00:24:56,119 --> 00:24:58,580
- they don't wanna see us unhappy.
- I wasn't unhappy.

286
00:24:58,663 --> 00:25:00,290
They're trying to help.

287
00:25:02,584 --> 00:25:04,127
That's what family does.

288
00:25:05,712 --> 00:25:08,340
- And I'm grateful for it. You understand?
- Yes.

289
00:25:11,843 --> 00:25:13,720
I know that you guys don't like this,

290
00:25:14,346 --> 00:25:15,847
but this is how it has to be.

291
00:25:18,767 --> 00:25:19,767
You trust your father?

292
00:25:20,477 --> 00:25:21,478
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

293
00:25:22,354 --> 00:25:23,355
Okay.

294
00:25:25,315 --> 00:25:29,361
