430
00:34:42,205 --> 00:34:43,956
Pleasure doing business with you.

431
00:34:44,999 --> 00:34:46,000
Thank you.

432
00:34:49,921 --> 00:34:51,339
Hey. We loaded up.

433
00:34:53,007 --> 00:34:54,133
Can we eat now?

434
00:34:56,302 --> 00:34:59,388
Here. Go get something.
I'm gonna take a look around.

435
00:35:39,637 --> 00:35:41,806
Don't be too loud. They just went to bed.

436
00:35:41,889 --> 00:35:44,892
I'm just trying to find out
what makes these guys so special.

437
00:35:45,393 --> 00:35:47,895
- Who?
- That Tejano band that we saw at the fair.

438
00:35:47,979 --> 00:35:50,898
Oh. The ones that packed the dance floor?

439
00:35:51,649 --> 00:35:52,733
The beat was nice.

440
00:35:53,526 --> 00:35:55,987
Los Dinos was an 11-piece orchestra

441
00:35:56,070 --> 00:35:58,364
playing mambos and cha-chas
