442
00:35:59,365 --> 00:36:01,325
but this…

443
00:36:03,619 --> 00:36:04,620
Times have changed.

444
00:36:05,246 --> 00:36:06,455
The music has changed.

445
00:36:07,748 --> 00:36:10,376
- Something hasn't changed.
<i>- </i>What?

446
00:36:10,459 --> 00:36:12,086
All the songs are in Spanish.

447
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:17,133
I don't know,
just Spanish is more romantic.

448
00:36:17,216 --> 00:36:18,217
Don't you think?

449
00:36:19,343 --> 00:36:22,513
Couples need to dance
and just fall in love.

450
00:36:23,931 --> 00:36:25,600
And that's never gonna change.

451
00:36:29,312 --> 00:36:31,189
You know what else will never change?

452
00:36:32,356 --> 00:36:33,356
What?

453
00:36:35,026 --> 00:36:37,486
My love for you, pretty lady.

454
00:36:37,570 --> 00:36:39,238
- Oh, yeah?
